dl.dd:


Note:
SIF_Message schemas define every data object element as optional per SIF's Publish/Subscribe and SIF Request/Response Models; 
DataModel schemas maintain the cardinality of all data object elements.

ul.li:
An element or attribute of type IdRefType can be defined that consists of the referenced object name concatenated with RefId, e.g., StudentPersonalRefId
(a reference to the object identifier/primary key/RefId of a StudentPersonal
object);
